{"type":"message","id":"a8bb5489","parentId":"23768bf3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T17:53:03.493Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<file name=\"/tmp/rack_module_prompts/4_kimi-b.txt\">\nYou own the rack specs / registry migration.\n\nOwned files only:\n- UserScripts/projects/Main/ui/behaviors/rack_midisynth_specs.lua\n- UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/providers/parameter_targets.lua\n- UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/providers/rack_sources.lua\n- UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/rack_control_router.lua\n\nTask:\nRename rack-layer node terminology to rack-module terminology in your owned files only.\n\nCanonical renames:\n- NODE_SPECS -> RACK_MODULE_SPECS\n- RackLayout.makeNodeSpec -> RackLayout.makeRackModuleSpec\n- RackLayout.makeNodeInstance -> RackLayout.makeRackModuleInstance\n- nodeSpecs() -> rackModuleSpecs()\n- nodeSpecById() -> rackModuleSpecById()\n- isNodeDeletable() -> isRackModuleDeletable()\n- spliceNode() -> spliceRackModule()\n- insertNodeAtVisualSlot() -> insertRackModuleAtVisualSlot()\n- __midiSynthDynamicNodeSpecs -> __midiSynthDynamicModuleSpecs\n- from.nodeId / to.nodeId -> from.moduleId / to.moduleId where these are rack connection endpoints\n- rackState.nodes / state.nodes -> modules where this is rack state\n\nCritical constraints:\n- Same repo, owned files only.\n- Do not touch runtime integrator files.\n- Do not rename non-rack graph node terminology.\n- Never run builds.\n- Do not run cmake, ninja, standalone app, VST, or other invasive commands.\n- Verify only with luac -p, rg, safe python.\n\nExemplars:\n- `local NODE_SPECS = { RackLayout.makeNodeSpec { ... } }`\n  becomes\n  `local RACK_MODULE_SPECS = { RackLayout.makeRackModuleSpec { ... } }`\n- dynamic globals move from `__midiSynthDynamicNodeSpecs` to `__midiSynthDynamicModuleSpecs`\n- endpoint fields become `moduleId`\n\nUseful references:\n- @agent-docs/active/plans/260402_rack_module_migration_tmux_delegation.md\n- @/tmp/rack_module_migration_inventory.md\n\nValidation:\n- `luac -p` each owned lua file\n- `rg` old symbols in owned files only\n\nReport:\n1. files changed\n2. exact renames completed\n3. unresolved cross-file dependencies\n4. risk/hotspots\n\n</file>\nRead the attached worker brief fully. Summarize your owned files, hard constraints, and first steps. Do not edit any files until I send GO."}],"timestamp":1775152383469}}
