ll check the inventory and active plan documents to understand the full context of this migration.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## Summary of Worker Brief\n\n### Owned Files (4 total)\n1. `UserScripts/projects/Main/ui/behaviors/rack_midisynth_specs.lua`\n2. `UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/providers/parameter_targets.lua`\n3. `UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/providers/rack_sources.lua`\n4. `UserScripts/projects/Main/lib/modulation/rack_control_router.lua`\n\n### Task\nRename rack-layer **node** terminology to **rack-module** terminology within owned files only.\n\n### Canonical Renames to Apply\n| Old Symbol | New Symbol |\n|------------|------------|\n| `NODE_SPECS` | `RACK_MODULE_SPECS` |\n| `RackLayout.makeNodeSpec` | `RackLayout.makeRackModuleSpec` |\n| `RackLayout.makeNodeInstance` | `RackLayout.makeRackModuleInstance` |\n| `nodeSpecs()` | `rackModuleSpecs()` |\n| `nodeSpecById()` | `rackModuleSpecById()` |\n| `isNodeDeletable()` | `isRackModuleDeletable()` |\n| `spliceNode()` | `spliceRackModule()` |\n| `insertNodeAtVisualSlot()` | `insertRackModuleAtVisualSlot()` |\n| `__midiSynthDynamicNodeSpecs` | `__midiSynthDynamicModuleSpecs` |\n| `from.nodeId` / `to.nodeId` (endpoints) | `from.moduleId` / `to.moduleId` |\n| `rackState.nodes` / `state.nodes` (rack state) | `modules` |\n\n### Hard Constraints\n- **Owned files only** - do not touch runtime integrator files\n- **No non-rack graph node terminology** - careful not to rename generic graph nodes\n- **Never run builds** - no cmake, ninja, standalone, VST\n- **Verification only via** `luac -p`, `rg`, safe python\n\n### Required Report\n1. Files changed\n2. Exact renames completed\n3. Unresolved cross-file dependencies\n4. Risk/hotspots\n\n---\n\n**Waiting for GO signal before proceeding.**\n\nI'll first read the owned files to assess current state and plan the edits. Want me to do that now or wait until GO?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding-plan","model":"k